<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ subject }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3E6A8A;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .status-activated {
            background-color: #dcfce7;
            color: #166534;
        }
        .status-deactivated {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            color: #991b1b;
        }
        .content {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .reason-box {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-left: 4px solid #3E6A8A;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3E6A8A, #5C8BA5);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5270, #4A7A95);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">CrediScore</div>
            <h1>Account Status Update</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{ name }},</p>
            
            <p>We wanted to inform you that your CrediScore account status has been updated.</p>

            <div class="status-badge status-{{ status }}">
                {% if status === 'activated' %}
                    ✅ Account Activated Successfully
                {% else %}
                    ⚠️ Account Deactivated
                {% endif %}
            </div>

            {% if status === 'activated' %}
            <p><strong>What this means:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>✅ You can now log in to your account</li>
                <li>🏠 Access your dashboard and profile</li>
                <li>🏢 Browse and review businesses</li>
                <li>⭐ Build your reputation score</li>
                <li>📊 Track your activity and achievements</li>
            </ul>
            {% else %}
            <p><strong>What this means:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>❌ You cannot log in to your account</li>
                <li>🚫 Access to platform features is restricted</li>
                <li>📧 You will not receive platform notifications</li>
            </ul>
            {% endif %}

            {% if reason %}
            <div class="reason-box">
                <h3>📋 Additional Information:</h3>
                <p>{{ reason }}</p>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            <p>If you have any questions about this change or need assistance, our support team is here to help.</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{ appUrl }}/contact" class="cta-button">💬 Contact Support</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-info">
            <h3>💬 Need Help?</h3>
            <p>Our support team is always here to assist you. Don't hesitate to reach out if you have any questions:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>📧 Email: support@crediscore.com</li>
                <li>📞 Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567</li>
                <li>🌐 Visit: <a href="{{ appUrl }}/support">{{ appUrl }}/support</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent to {{ email }}</p>
            <p>&copy; {{ year }} CrediScore. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{ appUrl }}/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                <a href="{{ appUrl }}/terms">Terms of Service</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
